      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能对金融稳定的风险已经成为央行的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ai-risks-to-financial-stability-are-already-a-central-bank-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位央行行长在周二的会议上表示，人工智能工具的发展对金融稳定构成的危险已经开始成为人们的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ai-risks-to-financial-stability-are-already-a-central-bank-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 15:54:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌前首席执行官施密特表示他考虑购买 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/schmidt-says-he-weighed-buying-tiktok-from-its-chinese-owners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌前首席执行官埃里克·施密特 (Eric Sc​​hmidt) 表示，他曾考虑过收购 TikTok 的可能性，但已经放弃了试图从中国所有者手中收购这款流行视频共享应用的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/schmidt-says-he-weighed-buying-tiktok-from-its-chinese-owners</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 15:08:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
